Class Application

java.lang.Object
processing.core.PApplet
core.Application
All Implemented Interfaces:
PConstants
public class Application
extends PApplet

Graphics Designer 9000

A basic graphics design software written in Java using Processing.

It has basic shape creation and edition functions, along with layer that can be rearranged and toggled on and off.
Version:
1
Author:
rollonit, Klemens Fliri
